// both failed RUNTIME_ERROR on all 16 workloads.  Likely root cause: float
// hashing in unordered_map is fragile (std::hash<float> is defined but two
// float values that compare == may not hash identically across compiler
// versions / optimization levels).  Fix: linear-search vector of pairs — at
// most 16 distinct rope_theta values, so O(16) per lookup is negligible.
//
