// rounds to fp32; each thread does exp2f(i*c).  Worst-case relative error is
// ~2.7e-6, and because inv_freq <= 1 the absolute error is the same, giving
// >=3x margin under the 1e-5 atol gate and clearing the 1e-5 rtol gate for all
// 64 elements.

